title: Jets complete second interviews with Darrell Bevell, Greg Roman for OC job

sources.name: Yahoo Sports NFL
sources.title: Jets complete second interviews with Darrell Bevell, Greg Roman for OC job
sources.description: The Jets have completed in-person interviews with Darrell Bevell and Greg Roman for their offensive coordinator position, the team announced Monday night.
